T.H.U.N.D.E.R.
--------------

Don't ask me what it stands for, I just think project names look neater with .'s after each letter.
Thunder is meant to be an automated installer for Gentoo Linux, although I believe it to be sufficiently
generic enough to be adapted to most any install. There is documentation being worked on, don't worry,
and I'll be getting an actual website and mailing lists setup
